OL,3,CBoy, 15, guilty of murder after
OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of murdering Muhammad Hassam
OL,8,FAli by stabbing him in the heart in
OL,9,FBirmingham city centre.
OL,11,FAli, 17, died in hospital hours after
OL,12,Fhe and his friend were followed by two
OL,13,Fmasked males before he was fatally
OL,14,Fstabbed as they sat in Victoria Square
OL,15,Fon January 20.
OL,17,FTwo 15-year-olds, who cannot be named
OL,18,Fbecause of their age, have been on
OL,19,Ftrial for the 17-year-old's murder and
OL,20,Fpossession of a knife at Coventry
OL,21,FCrown Court.
