OL,3,CBoy, 15, guilty of murder after
OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FA jury of six men and six women took
OL,7,Fjust over four hours to return
OL,8,Funanimous verdicts on Friday.
OL,10,FThey found the youth who carried out
OL,11,Fthe fatal attack guilty of murder and
OL,12,Fpossessing a knife and his friend, who
OL,13,Fwas standing nearby when the stabbing
OL,14,Fhappened, guilty of manslaughter and
OL,15,Fpossessing a knife.
