OL,3,CBoy, 15, guilty of murder after
OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FThe court heard Ali and his friend had
OL,7,Fgot hot chocolate at a coffee shop
OL,8,Fbefore heading to the square, where
OL,9,Fthey "simply sat down chatting and
OL,10,Fusing their phones" when they were
OL,11,Fapproached by the two youths "as if
OL,12,Ffrom nowhere".
