OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FThey had followed them from Grand
OL,7,FCentral Shopping Centre and through
OL,8,FNew Street before confronting Ali and
OL,9,Fhis friend at Victoria Square and did
OL,10,Fnot introduce themselves when they
OL,11,Fapproached, instead asking Ali and his
OL,12,Ffriend if they knew who had "jumped a
OL,13,Fmate" of theirs a week before, and
OL,14,Fwhere they came from.
