OL,3,CBoy, 15, guilty of murder after
OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FAfter a conversation lasting about
OL,7,Ffour minutes, in which the killer
OL,8,Falleged Ali and his friend told them
OL,9,Fto "f*** off" and "p**s off", Ali
OL,10,Fallegedly said: "Bro, I don't know
OL,11,Fwhat you're talking about, you're
OL,12,Fp*sing me off", which prompted one of
OL,13,Fthe youths to pull out a large knife
OL,14,Fand stab him in the chest before they
OL,15,Fboth fled.
