OL,3,CBoy, 15, guilty of murder after
OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FGiving evidence, the youth, who had
OL,7,Fthe knife in his trousers before
OL,8,Fstabbing Ali and was wearing a Covid-
OL,9,Fstyle face mask, a hat and gloves,
OL,10,Ftold the court he only pulled out the
OL,11,Fknife to "scare" Ali and his friend,
OL,12,Fand that he did not intend to
OL,13,Fseriously harm or kill anyone.
OL,15,FHe said he carried a knife when he
OL,16,Fwent to busy places like Birmingham
OL,17,Fcity centre for protection as he had
OL,18,Fbeen attacked several times before,
OL,19,Fand that he felt "regretful and upset"
OL,20,Fwhen he learned he had killed Ali.
