OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FThe other youth, who did not give
OL,7,Fevidence during the trial but spoke to
OL,8,Fpolice in an interview after he was
OL,9,Farrested, said he had been "shocked
OL,10,Fand crying" after the attack, claiming
OL,11,Fhe did not know his friend had a knife
OL,12,Fon him until he produced it during the
OL,13,Fconfrontation.
OL,15,FHe said he tried to convince the
OL,16,Fstabber to leave Ali and his friend
OL,17,Falone so they could go and get food as
OL,18,Fplanned, but he wanted to confront
OL,19,Fthem about an alleged incident that
OL,20,Fhad happened previously.
