OL,3,CBoy, 15, guilty of murder after
OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FHe also said he had never seen Ali or
OL,7,Fhis friend before and only went along
OL,8,Fwith the killer in case he "got
OL,9,Fbattered".
OL,11,FThere were sobs from the public
OL,12,Fgallery as the jury returned their
OL,13,Fverdicts on Friday.
OL,15,FJudge Mr Justice Garnham had to ask
OL,16,Ffor silence as he addressed the jury
OL,17,Ffollowing their deliberations.
