OL,3,CBoy, 15, guilty of murder after
OL,4,CBirmingham city centre stabbing
OL,6,FHe said: "Thank you very much, it has
OL,7,Fbeen obvious to everyone that you have
OL,8,Fbeen following and listening to the
OL,9,Farguments.
OL,11,F"That is now formally the end of your
OL,12,Fwork in this case."
OL,14,FMr Justice Garnham also thanked West
OL,15,FMidlands Police for their work on the
OL,16,Fcase, adding: "This has not been an
OL,17,Feasy case to try."
OL,19,FThe youths will be sentenced on a date
OL,20,Fto be fixed in early October.
